  = section "*whāb “give”" do
    %p The root *whāb “give” is only truly irregular in <i>katab</i>, where most forms lose either the #{template "C1"} *w or the #{template "C2"} *h. In other scales its irregularities are predictable using the normal rules of weak roots.
