      %li <i>katab</i>: #{t "άμαρ", "'amar"} / #{t "μώρ", "mār"} “say”
      %li <i>nuktāb</i>: #{t "νυαμώρ", "nu'amār"} “be said”
      %li <i>taktēb</i>: #{t "ταηαμήρ", "tahamēr"} “say together, say in unison”
